      <div class="col-md-7">
        <h2 class="lined-heading"><span>Send a message</span></h2>
        <p>To make any enquiry about AHA-足Rooms please complete the form below and send it. You can also email us directly info@aha-rooms.com. or call us 0034足971509183 or 0034603145782 and we will be very happy to help.</p>
        <div id="message"></div>
        <!-- Error message display -->
